highlights.text: EM XINH "SAY HI" has the most spots on Top Songs Vietnam. “GÃ SĂN CÁ” is the highest at #10.
“Âm Thầm Bên Em” by Sơn Tùng M-TP has been on Top Songs Vietnam the longest, at 1694 days straight.
“Ngày Này Năm Ấy” by Việt Anh is the highest new entry on Top Songs Vietnam at #191.
“Anh Muốn Nhìn Thấy Em” by The Wind and Dangrangto is the biggest gainer on Top Songs Vietnam, up 56 spots at #65.
